Package nl.utwente.jmlplugin

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JMLCompletionTest
    Test for the code completion part of the plugin.
    JMLFileType
    Class the represents the JML file type.
    JMLIcons
    Class that holds the references to the Icons used in the plugin.
    JMLIntegrationTest
    Does an integration test on the annotators
    JMLLanguage
    Class that represents the JML language in IntelliJ
    JMLLexerAdapter
    Class that links the JFlex lexer to the java classes.
    JMLMultiHostInjector
    Injects JML into Java comments.
    JMLParserDefinition
    Class that defines parser behaviour for the JML parser implementation.
    JMLParsingTest
    Tests that the parsers generate correct parse trees and error elements at the correct places
    JMLSemanticsAnnotatorTest
    Tests that correct semantic errors are given
    JMLSyntaxAnnotatorTest
    Tests that correct syntax errors are given
    JMLTypeAnnotatorTest
    Tests that all the type checking is done correctly so that the error messages are shown at the correct spot and that they are only shown when there is an actual type error
